# Restaurant Menu UI

This project was created as part of the CodSoft UI/UX Internship.

## Figma Design Link
https://www.figma.com/design/oz4bLVjKtfrTy9hgsuJaJy/Restaurant-Menu?node-id=0-1&t=MNPY1qrlHDKNn5Dz-1

## Features
- Category navigation
- Search bar
- Food cards with images, descriptions, and prices
- Offer banner
- Responsive desktop layout

